projectGridLines.title: Development Intern (Engineering Team)
projectGridLines.description:
Description: Students will work as a part of development project teams. They

will be assigned projects based on their current hands-on experience, courses

done and what they feel passionate about.

Skill sets: Java, Golang, ReactJS, Data Structures, Algorithms

Expected learning: *B2B Enterprise Platform Product development

*Learn how customers use Eltropy products and how they benefit

Specific courses required for project execution: Data structures, Algorithms,

Java. CS projects.
